  original project.
</p>

<h2>CoCitizen's role</h2>
<p>
  The original public upstream project is no longer actively maintained. CoCitizen stepped in as
  steward of the public version — taking on current deployments, adding functionality to
  run multiple simultaneous scenarios from a single instance, and rebuilding the deployment
  documentation so that self-hosted instances are actually practical.
</p>
<p>
  RisingStack, the original development firm, continues to contribute improvements under a separate contract.
</p>

